{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 955446, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "手中有点权利，就颐气指使，之前也很讨厌驾校驾练，还让我们给他买烟。", "timestamp": 1611304989, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955448, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "你的理解是正确的", "timestamp": 1611305048, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955453, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "驾校教练真的稂莠不齐......", "timestamp": 1611305080, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955456, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "教练就是工具人，过两天就再也不用见面了", "timestamp": 1611305114, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955457, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz去年也是，满口粗话实在忍不了，直接开怼，后来就换教练了", "timestamp": 1611305127, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955460, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "硬气点，你交了钱。驾校教练都是遇弱则强，上次同车的一个大姐把他怼得没脾气", "timestamp": 1611305174, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955468, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "是啊，教练的工作和老师很相似，但是我认为很多教练的素质和教学水平达不到老师的标准。。。来驾校以前从来没受过这种气", "timestamp": 1611305226, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955504, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "难道不是会开车懂考试得分点的都能当驾校教练吗？有一定学历的教师群体素质都尚且得不到保证，更何况毫无门槛的驾校教练？", "timestamp": 1611305470, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 955548, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 193748, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "忍着吧pat 